{
  "stem": "4764.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Apart from all those years ago in Hungary, I no longer eat it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had not a very happy teenage years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to-- after this, we graduated from this one room to a small flat in Bondi Junction.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I was the only child, and my parents went to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after school, I used to-- my mother worked for [INAUDIBLE], which was a manufacturing company, as a dispatcher.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was afraid to stay in the flat by myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So after school, I used to go by tram to the city and wait for her to come out of the factory at 5:30, whatever it was, and come home with her.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I couldn't stay home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I did this for years, which is most unusual for, for, for someone like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had this sort of bond with my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I couldn't be separated, apart from the time I went to school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The rest of the time, I couldn't be left alone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I, I had a big problem with that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I think that affected me, oh, I suppose a lot, in lots of ways-- in relationships and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But this fear of being alone, I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That must have stemmed from my upbringing, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it affected me in lots of other ways.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because this bond that was a very-- I mean, I suppose it was a very good bond, between mother and son.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But it became unhealthy in later life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because my mother then became the-- as she became older, she became more dependent on me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Whereas I broke loose from this-- from these shackles, I suppose, she withdrew into it as she got older.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And therefore, I had to look after her.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
